        <abstract> 
<p>Pleased to hear that EK agrees to CD’s request to have article on Erasmus Darwin translated. Will wait for EK’s enlargement. Has decided submission to <hi rend="italic">Fortnightly Review</hi> would be useless.</p> 
            <p>Warns against Anna Seward’s biography of Dr Darwin.</p>
        </abstract>
